@startuml
title Proxy

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Provide a surrogate/placeholder to control access (lazy loading, remote, protection).

**Use when**: Control access, defer expensive operations, add caching/auth.

**Key participants**: Subject, RealSubject, Proxy.
endlegend

interface Subject {
  +request()
}

class RealSubject
class Proxy {
  -real : RealSubject
  +request()
}

Subject <|.. RealSubject
Subject <|.. Proxy
Proxy o-- RealSubject
@enduml